headline: Does Costco’s Removal of Xbox Signal a Tipping Point for Its Stock in 2025?
summary: Thinking about what to do with your Costco Wholesale stock? You're not alone. Whether you're a long-time believer in the warehouse giant or just considering an investment, there's good reason to keep a close eye on Costco's story. Over the past year, the stock has climbed 5.0%. While the year-to-date return sits at a modest 0.8%, those who stayed invested over the past three or five years have seen gains of 99.1% and 174.2%, respectively. headline: Trinity Energy Delivers Blueprint for Large-Scale Energy Independence at Costco’s Largest Distribution Center
summary: SNOHOMISH, Wash., October 02, 2025--Trinity Energy (Trinity), a leading provider of turnkey sustainable energy solutions, announced the successful pre-commissioning of a comprehensive solar, battery storage, and electric vehicle (EV) charging solution at Costco Wholesale’s Mira Loma and Ontario distribution centers in California, marking a significant step toward energy independence for one of the world’s leading retailers.
